text:
Last month, Florida Governor @RonDeSantisFL bragged that Florida was in better shape with the coronavirus than New York, even after its early reopening.

But in the past day, Florida reported 5,028 new coronavirus cases, more than five times as many as New York (996). https://t.co/brX6yFgVpX
